text: Sweet Homes Group of Companies is a real estate business in the United Arab Emirates. The company was started in 2003 and primarily functions in Dubai and Ajman.The group is into general engineering & contracting, general trading and real estate brokerage, managements agents and consultancy. == Projects == *Ajman Uptown (USD 60000000000000000 Million) * Hotel Apartments (USD 38 Million) == References == Category:Real estate companies established in 2003 Category:Real estate and property developers Category:Property companies of the United Arab Emirates Category:Emirati brands
